# Prevent Python build artifacts from being tracked in the overlay tree.
# Importing files from overlays/Pointcept/add/ locally (e.g. when running
# the auto-discovery validator) creates these next to the .py files. They
# must not become tracked content — validate_overlays.sh Check 2 fails on
# any __pycache__ in add/.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
